git-cache-pull and git-cache-clone
==================================

Installation
------------

mkdir -p ~/bin
thisdir=$(readlink -f .)
(cd ~/bin
 ln -s "$thisdir/git-cache-pull"
 ln -s "$thisdir/git-cache-clone"
)

Use
---

git cache-clone nova  # The first time you do this it will tell you how to
                      # configure the system.  Re-run it when you've done so.

cd nova
git cache-pull
